channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Ole Miss Rebels Unveil Powder Blue-Accented Road Jersey
item.description: Ole Miss unveiled the first powder blue-accented road jersey in school history on Monday morning, granting the wishes of a large portion of the Rebels' fanbase.

item.title: MTV's 'Real World' Star Sarah Becker Dead at 52 By Suicide
item.description: Sarah Becker -- a reality television star who appeared on MTV's "The Real World" -- has died by suicide ... TMZ has learned. A family member of Becker confirmed the tragic news to TMZ ... telling us she died early last week at her home in Illinois.…

item.description: Donald Trump says he learned people could get away with abhorrent behavior as long as they had good ratings like he did on "The Apprentice" ... according to a bombshell book. The ex-prez made the claims during an interview with Variety…

item.title: Tennessee Volunteers’ New “Smokey Grey” Alternate Jerseys Leak
item.description: For the second year in a row, Tennessee had its new “Smokey Grey” alternate jersey leaked by Dick’s Sporting Goods after the retailer had a mannequin wearing the jersey on display on Friday afternoon.
